title: 이달의소녀탐구 #102 (LOONA TV #102)
summary:
The girls arrive in Busan for shooting!
0:07 -- *blinkblink* ViVi looks tired.
0:09 -- ViVi goat laugh. Is that an overdub? Did she really laugh like a goat?
0:11 -- ViVi thinks “Busan looks like Singapore”. ViVi’s never been to Singapore!
0:26 -- HaSeul laments the curse of HaSeul
0:29 -- ViVi prays to HaSeul to end her cursed rains
0:41 -- HaSeul does a big “okay” symbol
0:45 -- “Hwaiting!” HaSeul and ViVi. Slightly more convincing than last episode.
